The woman testified she did not realise her husband was planning an attack when he asked to 
meet her boyfriend in person one night in December, 2008.

'All I am gonna do is shake his hand,' she said he told her, according to the Register.

But the break room became a makeshift torture chamber, with McClain using two 
guns and a knife he had brought to the meeting, Christl said.

